data.title: Eagles Of Death Metal To Start Recording New Album Soon?
data.meta_description: Josh Homme could be entering the studio to record the new Eagles Of Death Metal album even before his main band – Queens Of The Stone Age – release their much anticipated record …Like Clockwork in June.
